You should:

possess a recognized university degree or above in Public Relations, Journalism, Communications or related discipline;
have at least 5 years of relevant and solid experience in public relations, events management, media relations, corporate communications, corporate social responsibility and community engagement;
have proven experience in engaging government bodies, NGOs, community groups; arts and culture groups;
possess strong interpersonal and communication skills, be a good team player with creativity and dynamism, attention to details, and able to multi-task and meet tight deadlines and work under pressure;
